org.htwk.graphplot.expression.core

Interface Expression

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Add, Divide, Function, Minimum, Multiply, Negative, Number, Operation, Power, Sinus, SquareRoot, Subtract

    public interface Expression
    This interface describes the most generalized form of a calculable object. The mathematical term is supposed to be resolved with the use of a decorator pattern and this is the generalization.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Sophie Eckenstaler, René Martin
